---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service" description="Terms of Service for ASH - Secure Messaging Application">
  <div class="py-16 sm:py-24">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 bg-brand-subtle text-brand-light text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider rounded-full mb-6">
        Legal
      </span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-text-secondary text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Last updated: January 22, 2025
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <article class="prose-content space-y-8">

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-border">1. Agreement to Terms</h2>
          <div class="text-text-secondary space-y-4">
            <p>
              By downloading, installing, or using ASH ("the App"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service ("Terms"). If you do not agree to these Terms, do not use the App.
            </p>
            <p>
              ASH is developed and published by <strong class="text-white">Monadial</strong> ("Developer", "we", "us").
            </p>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-border">2. Description of Service</h2>
          <div class="text-text-secondary space-y-4">
            <p>
              ASH is a secure, ephemeral messaging application that uses One-Time Pad (OTP) encryption for communication between two parties. The App is designed for high-security, low-frequency communication.
            </p>
            <p>Key characteristics of the service:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
              <li>Messages are encrypted using One-Time Pad encryption</li>
              <li>Encryption keys are generated during an in-person ceremony</li>
              <li>There is no key recovery or key escrow mechanism</li>
              <li>Messages are ephemeral and cannot be recovered once deleted</li>
              <li>The service requires an in-person meeting to establish communication</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-border">3. User Responsibilities</h2>
          <div class="text-text-secondary space-y-4">
            <p>By using ASH, you agree to:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
              <li>Use the App only for lawful purposes</li>
              <li>Not use the App to transmit illegal, harmful, or offensive content</li>
              <li>Take responsibility for safeguarding your device and encryption keys</li>
              <li>Understand that lost keys cannot be recovered</li>
              <li>Comply with all applicable laws and regulations in your jurisdiction</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-border">4. No Key Recovery</h2>
          <div class="text-text-secondary space-y-4">
            <p>
              <strong class="text-warning">Important:</strong> ASH is designed with no key recovery mechanism. This is an intentional security feature, not a limitation.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
              <li>If you lose your device or delete the App, your encryption keys are permanently lost</li>
              <li>The Developer cannot recover, reset, or regenerate your keys</li>
              <li>There is no "forgot password" or account recovery option</li>
              <li>You are solely responsible for maintaining access to your device</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-border">5. Privacy and Data</h2>
          <div class="text-text-secondary space-y-4">
            <p>
              ASH is designed with privacy as a core principle. Please review our <a href="/privacy" class="text-brand hover:text-brand-light">Privacy Policy</a> for detailed information about data handling.
            </p>
            <p>Key points:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 ml-4">
              <li>Messages are end-to-end encrypted with One-Time Pad encryption</li>
              <li>The relay server cannot decrypt your messages</li>
              <li>No user accounts or identifiers are required</li>
              <li>Minimal metadata is processed, and only transiently</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-border">6. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <div class="text-text-secondary space-y-4">
