              <li>The App is free of viruses or other harmful components</li>
              <li>The security provided will meet your specific requirements</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-border">8. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <div class="text-text-secondary space-y-4">
            <p>
