              <li>Loss of encrypted messages due to key loss</li>
              <li>Inability to communicate due to pad exhaustion</li>
              <li>Any consequences arising from the security model of the App</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 pb-2 border-b border-border">9. Prohibited Uses</h2>
